cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SI 

The paper deals with a learning task in a convolutional neural network, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). The proposed scale regularization method also falls under the category of regularization techniques, which is a common topic in the sub-category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of variational methods is also a common topic in the sub-category of statistical learning (cs.SI).
